@startuml Recruiter_Dashboard

title Recruiter - Dashboard (Module D)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "DASHBOARD" {
    usecase "View Recruiter\nDashboard" as D20
}

Recruiter --> D20: 1. Go to dashboard
D20 --> D20: View my jobs summary
D20 --> D20: View applications summary
D20 --> D20: View interview schedule
D20 --> D20: View notifications

note right of D20
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
